		<a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=13&mode=details&type=races'>Paladin</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=19&mode=details&type=races'>Wizard</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=9&mode=details&type=races'>Cleric</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=1&mode=details&type=races'>Druid</a>
     </font>
    
    </td>
  </tr>
